====== H994: בִּי (bîy) ======

===== Source =====

perhaps from  H1158  (in the sense of asking); properly, a request; used only adverbially (always with 'my Lord');

===== Meaning =====

oh that! ;  with leave , or  if it please

===== Definitions =====

  - oh that!
  - with leave
  - if it please

===== Usage =====

alas, O, oh.
